INSTRUCTIONS
================
* To compile FFMPEG

./configure --arch=x86 --enable-libmp3lame --enable-libx264 --enable-nonfree --enable-gpl --disable-doc

* The directory 'ffmpeg' includes the plugin filter. To compile it just run
  /configure as usual.

* The directory 'vfilter_plugin' includes the implementation of the logo 
  detection filter. OpenCV needs to be installed to compile it.

bin/ffmpeg -qscale 2 -i share/videos/IMG_0092.MOV -vf plugin=./logo.so:./share/logos/Dior.jpg -y out.mov



